com.microsoft.azure.iothub.transport.amqps

Class AmqpsIotHubConnectionBaseHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.BaseHandler
      • com.microsoft.azure.iothub.transport.amqps.AmqpsIotHubConnectionBaseHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.CoreHandler, org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.Handler

    public final class AmqpsIotHubConnectionBaseHandler
extends org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.BaseHandler
    Instance of the QPID-Proton-J BaseHandler class that overrides the events needed to handle receiving and sending operations. Contains and sets connection parameters, maintains the layers of the AMQP protocol and creates and sets SASL authentication for the transport.

                                        String sasToken,

        Constructor to set up connection parameters and initialize handshaker and flow controller for the transport.
        Parameters:
        hostName - The address string of the IoT Hub (example: AAA.BBB.CCC).
        userName - The username string to use SASL authentication (example: user@sas.[hostName]).
        sasToken - The SAS token string.
        deviceID - The ID for the associated device.
        parentIotHubConnection - The parent AmqpsIotHubConnection object.
